<B>__{butch and bob}
<A>__{chuck the small. bob looks for a place to hide. closeup phillip screaming at the top of his lungs. closeup butch staring straight ahead at phillip. butch doesn't even flinch, standing his ground in the middle of the road, staring straight into phillip's oncoming face.}
